maintext:
What Time Does the New England Patriots Super Bowl Game Start?
What: Super Bowl LIII
Who: New England Patriots vs. Los Angeles Rams
Where: Mercedes Benz Stadium, Atlanta
Kickoff: 6:30 p.m.
National Anthem: Gladys Knight
Halftime show: Maroon 5, joined by Travis Scott and Big Boi
On TV: All coverage is on CBS (Channel 4). Pregame show begins at 2 p.m.
Online streaming: CBS All Access, NFL Game Pass, Yahoo Sports, Fubo
Radio: 98.5 The Sports Hub
